    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A journey through the world's end ripe with exploration, fights, and an enthralling story.<br>Travel through the beautiful pixel-art world as the adventure of a sword and a bird unfolds.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/f7834fd0804361fe0110b37df21dcd89.poster.avif?t=1736823588\" width=362 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/f7834fd0804361fe0110b37df21dcd89.webm?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/f7834fd0804361fe0110b37df21dcd89.mp4?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Machina of the Farthest is a &quot;warping-boomerang 2D action game&quot; set in a universe drawn with painstakingly crafted pixel art.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/659872b9e4257389edae32ae587e2dae.poster.avif?t=1736823588\" width=494 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/659872b9e4257389edae32ae587e2dae.webm?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/659872b9e4257389edae32ae587e2dae.mp4?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Plot</h2>Not long after civilization has been destroyed, the world is full of Mechanisms, strange creatures that threaten any attempt humans may make to rebuild.<br><br>A girl called Machina wakes up without her memories. Armed with the &quot;Blue Sword,&quot; which lets her warp to wherever she throws it and with her childhood friend Kamiki by her side, she starts on a journey to get her memories back.<br><br>The two slowly rebuild their lost connection, unaware of the tragedy she has forgotten.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Sword's Powers</h2>.Machina's Blue Sword is more than just a weapon: it has the power to immediately warp her to wherever she throws it.<br>You will need both brains and brawn to use it as the key that will open your path forward.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/7b384545754401fb970c3bba5b180826.poster.avif?t=1736823588\" width=466 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/7b384545754401fb970c3bba5b180826.webm?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386000/extras/7b384545754401fb970c3bba5b180826.mp4?t=1736823588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
